works.description: Designed by Swedish firm Gray Design and Strand Craft, the Strand Craft Limousine Beach Cruiser primarily targets the luxury hotel chains that want to impress their rich clientele with a unique service. Offering the ultimate in beachside transport, the car has been designed to transport the super rich from their luxurious hotel suites or private residences to the beaches in utmost comfort. The 2012 Strand Craft Limousine Beach Cruiser has been built with focus on the maximum in-car exposure to the sun, and features a range of stylish cues such as the canvas roof, chromed hubcaps and wooden inlays.
